<% layout('./layouts/boilerplate') %>
<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">Last updated: December 2024</p>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3">Information We Collect</h3>
                    <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, make a booking, or contact us for support.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Personal information (name, email, phone number)</li>
                        <li>Payment information (processed securely by our payment partners)</li>
                        <li>Booking preferences and history</li>
                        <li>Communication records with our support team</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h3>
                    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Process and manage your bookings</li>
                        <li>Provide customer support and respond to your inquiries</li>
                        <li>Send you booking confirmations and important updates</li>
                        <li>Improve our services and user experience</li>
                        <li>Prevent fraud and ensure platform security</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3">Information Sharing</h3>
                    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties except:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>To hotel partners to process your bookings</li>
                        <li>To payment processors for secure transaction processing</li>
                        <li>When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
                        <li>With your explicit consent</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3">Data Security</h3>
                    <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Encryption of sensitive data in transit and at rest</li>
                        <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
                        <li>Limited access to personal information on a need-to-know basis</li>
                        <li>Secure payment processing through trusted partners</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3">Your Rights</h3>
                    <p>You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access and review your personal information</li>
                        <li>Request corrections to inaccurate information</li>
                        <li>Delete your account and associated data</li>
                        <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
                        <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3">Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@travelnest.com<br>
                        <strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (555) 123-4567<br>
                        <strong>Address:</strong> 123 Tourism Avenue, Travel City, TC 12345
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>